        <div class="accordion-heading">
          <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2">
            B.1. Ship's Crew
          </a>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-body collapse in">
          <div class="accordion-inner">
            <p>
                The vessel will be manned wholly by crew of Vietnamese nationality. Senior staff will be proficient in the English language.
            </p>
            <p>
                Key crew members - masters and mates - are recruited with previous container vessel service experience, and the engineer officers are well experienced in the vessel's engine / machinery types. Officers and ratings will be assigned from NII fleet and will be selected based on good service records and the right attitude for the job.
            </p>
            <p>
                Officers and ratings will hold the required government / international certification and will have attended all required safety and training courses. Refresher courses and additional training will be arranged whenever necessary during the crew's leave periods.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-group">
        <div class="accordion-heading">
